# Roles & Permissions Engine (v1.0 — frozen)

Administration → **Roles & Permissions** (`/admin/roles-permissions`)

Security backbone of Catalyst One. SUPER_ADMIN only (via `/admin` layout).

## Identity model (never mix)

1. User Type — Normal / Hybrid Employee (defaults only; not permissions)
2. Roles — unlimited custom roles
3. Permissions — View / Create-Edit / Admin per module (overrides role defaults)
4. Platform Access — Catalyst One | COMPASS | Both (independent)

## Governance

- Only Super Admin: create / edit / delete / clone roles & templates; grant/revoke Level-1 Role Admin delegation (non-recursive)
- Sensitive Admin confirmation for critical modules
- Never remove / deactivate last active Super Administrator
- User exit (Resigned/Archived) work transfer lives in Enterprise User Management
- Permanent non-editable security audit trail

## Source of truth

- Types: `src/types/roles-permissions-engine.ts`
- Constants / seeds: `src/constants/roles-permissions-engine`
- Store: `src/lib/roles-permissions-engine`
- UI: `src/components/catalyst-one/roles-permissions-engine`
- Permission module catalog shared with EUM: `EUM_PERMISSION_MODULES`
